1. Copy AnimeWatch-PyQt5 folder of the parent directory in this current working directory.

2. Rename AnimeWatch-PyQt5 folder to AnimeWatch_PyQt5.

3. Open Terminal in the current directory and execute 'python setup.py sdist'

4. Now 'dist' folder will be created and source distribution package will be built in it.

5. Go to dist folder and install the package using 'sudo pip3' command. It will install most of the python based dependencies and install the package.

7. Dependencies which needs to be installed manually for this Application to work correctly.

	1. PyQt5 (if it can't be installed via pip3, most important depndency)
	2. mpv
	3. mplayer
	4. sqlite3
	5. ffmpegthumbnailer
	6. curl
	7. wget
	8. libnotify
	9. libtorrent

6. Once the package is installed alongwith all the dependencies, open the terminal and run command 'animewatch' to open the application.